: "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1647359938", "stars": 7749, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 451225, "username": "imblues", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/imblues", "website": "www.jd.com", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "上海", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b87a/4d18/451225_mini.png?m=1626433658", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b87a/4d18/451225_normal.png?m=1626433658", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b87a/4d18/451225_large.png?m=1626433658", "created": 1572932721, "last_modified": 1626433658}, "last_reply_by": "f360family123", "last_touched": 1648105553, "title": "如果有 20 天的时间，学什么技术对将来发展有利呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/842460", "created": 1648040397, "deleted": 0, "content": "如题，2022 年有什么新的技术值得投入时间学习吗？\r\n欢迎大家一起来探讨。", "content_rendered": "<p>如题，2022 年有什么新的技术值得投入时间学习吗？\n欢迎大家一起来探讨。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1648040452, "replies": 51, "id": 842460}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 17953, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2107, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 426714, "username": "dropsio", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dropsio", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed91/71b5/426714_mini.png?m=1587987192", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed91/71b5/426714_normal.png?m=1587987192", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed91/71b5/426714_large.png?m=1587987192", "created": 1562208681, "last_modified": 1587987192}, "last_reply_by": "BlackJac95", "last_touched": 1648081122, "title": "关于 M1 买 13 寸 还是 14 寸的选择问题...", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/842394", "created": 1648024909, "deleted": 0, "content": "本人前端开发，原本有一台 15 寸的 14 年款 16G macbook pro ，现在也到了要退休的年纪了，想着换个新款，现在面临做选择题：\r\n\r\n* `first`：M1 13 寸 16G\r\n\r\n* `second`：M1 pro 14 寸 32G\r\n          \r\n一般来讲，14 寸的性能这么劲爆，没啥好考虑的，买就完事了；但奈何太丑，比较嫌弃;\r\n\r\n13 寸作为果厂最后一款高颜值 mac pro, 而且也是 M1 ，感觉性能应该不会太差，所以我还是比较倾向与选择 13 寸 的;\r\n\r\n纠结这两款的主要原因，就集中到了一点，内存...\r\n\r\n由于平时出现卡顿时，无法确定是因为设备老化还是内存不足，就判断不出 ` first ` 到底够不够日常丝滑开发所用（主要是平时没关注，想甩锅）。\r\n\r\n所以想求教一下用过 ` first ` 的各位前端大佬，到底丝不丝滑？\r\n\r\n也想了解一下其他开发大佬是怎么选择的呢？\r\n\r\n是选择 ` first ` 呢？还是放弃颜值，拥抱性能选择 ` second ` ?", "content_rendered": "<p>本人前端开发，原本有一台 15 寸的 14 年款 16G macbook pro ，现在也到了要退休的年纪了，想着换个新款，现在面临做选择题：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>first</code>：M1 13 寸 16G</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>second</code>：M1 pro 14 寸 32G</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>一般来讲，14 寸的性能这么劲爆，没啥好考虑的，买就完事了；但奈何太丑，比较嫌弃;</p>\n<p>13 寸作为果厂最后一款高颜值 mac pro, 而且也是 M1 ，感觉性能应该不会太差，所以我还是比较倾向与选择 13 寸 的;</p>\n<p>纠结这两款的主要原因，就集中到了一点，内存...</p>\n<p>由于平时出现卡顿时，无法确定是因为设备老化还是内存不足，就判断不出 <code>first</code> 到底够不够日常丝滑开发所用（主要是平时没关注，想甩锅）。</p>\n<p>所以想求教一下用过 <code>first</code> 的各位前端大佬，到底丝不丝滑？</p>\n<p>也想了解一下其他开发大佬是怎么选择的呢？</p>\n<p>是选择 <code>first</code> 呢？还是放弃颜值，拥抱性能选择 <code>second</code> ?</p>\n", "last_modified": 1648024909, "replies": 47, "id": 842394}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1647359938", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1647359938", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.